2013;;Tracks;;Australian;;John Curran;;Mia Wasikowska;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tracks_(2013_film);;In 1977, Robyn Davidson travels from Alice Springs across 2,700 kilometers (1,700 miles) of Australian deserts to the Indian Ocean with her dog and four camels.[6][7] National Geographic photographer Rick Smolan documents her journey.